node.text: Louise is one of my favorite names ever. And seeing sweet Louise’s reaction to my video message to her is exactly what I didn’t know I needed - a reminder of why I’m here: to connect with strangers. Thank you, Louise. Wish I could hug you. ❤️ (Had permission to post this)

node.text: So excited! I’ve created a brand new #Rossipe that’s super-delish & barely any @WW points! You’re gonna love this one! And you’re gonna love @WW‘s recently launched myWW+, their most holistic program ever! #WWPartner It gives us all the tools we need to track our food, water intake, sleep activity & mindset. You can find thousands of healthy recipes in the WW app- including my #Rossipe! Go to ww.com/Ross for a limited time offer and to find out more! (Link in bio). People following the WW program can expect to lose 1-2 lbs/week.

node.text: A big thanks to @AccessOnline & @Sib_Vicious for telling my story about learning from loss and trying to be the healthiest version of myself possible. My struggle is a universal one. If you, too, are a work in progress, we are in this together. ❤️

node.text: Karaoke tonight with friends. 🥰 We didn’t sing (I usually do), but it was so fun to sit in our little corner & hear people belt. Scott & I have been friends for nearly 20 years. I used to deliver his mail as an intern on The Tonight Show. Then, when I was happily thrust onto TV, he was there, guiding me every step of the way. We’ve been lifelong friends ever since. We should all be so lucky! ❤️

node.text: THANK YOU @televisionacad for nominating us again this year!!! Creating, hosting and producing TV has been my dream since I was just a little kid and I am grateful for every single second of this extraordinary journey. 🥰 Congrats to the entire hard working team at @RuPaulsDragRace, @worldofwonder, @vh1 & all the queens for an amazing season 13, filmed last summer under unparalleled & historic Covid restrictions. It’s an honor to work with you. ❤️ And congrats to all the other nominees! 🏆
